{"title":"Plugins","description":"Plugins","url":"/docs/addons","contributors":["jthoms1"],"headings":[{"id":"plugins","level":1,"text":"Plugins"},{"id":"stencil-sass","level":2,"text":"Stencil Sass"},{"id":"installing","level":3,"text":"Installing"},{"id":"options","level":3,"text":"Options"}],"srcPath":"./src/docs/tooling/plugins.md","content":"\n<h1 id=\"plugins\">\n  \n  Plugins\n  \n</h1>\n\n<h2 id=\"stencil-sass\">\n  <a class=\"heading-link\" href=\"#stencil-sass\"><app-icon name=\"link\"></app-icon>\n  Stencil Sass\n  </a>\n</h2>\n<p><code>@stencil/sass</code> is an npm package that enables to use <a href=\"https://sass-lang.com/\">Sass</a> in your web components built with Stencil. During development, this plugin will kick-in for .scss or .sass style urls, and precompile them to CSS.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"installing\">\n  <a class=\"heading-link\" href=\"#installing\"><app-icon name=\"link\"></app-icon>\n  Installing\n  </a>\n</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>In your project directory run <code>npm install @stencil/sass --save</code>.</li>\n<li>Require the plugin in your <code>stencil.config.ts</code> file.</li>\n<li>Add the plugin to your <code>plugins</code> array:</li>\n</ol>\n\n  <highlight-code-line >\n    <pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Config <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@stencil/core'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> sass <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@stencil/sass'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> config<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Config <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>    <span class=\"token function\">sass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n  </highlight-code-line>\n  \n<h3 id=\"options\">\n  <a class=\"heading-link\" href=\"#options\"><app-icon name=\"link\"></app-icon>\n  Options\n  </a>\n</h3>\n<p>Sass options can be passed to the plugin within <code>stencil.config.ts</code>, which are used directly by node-sass. Please reference the <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-sass\">node-sass documentation</a> for all available options.</p>\n\n  <highlight-code-line >\n    <pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Config <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@stencil/core'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> config<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Config <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">sass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> includePaths<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'/my-include-path'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n  </highlight-code-line>\n  "}